# ARP Poisoning Detection Rules
# Project: ARP Poisoning MITM Attack & Detection Lab
# Analyst: Chirayu Mahendra Palandurkar
# Note: Suricata 8 does not support native ARP rule signatures.
# These rules detect IP-level anomalies associated with ARP poisoning activity.
# For true Layer 2 ARP detection, use arpwatch on a dedicated network sensor.

alert ip any any -> any any (msg:"ARP Poisoning Detected"; detection_filter:track by_src, count 10, seconds 5; sid:9000001; rev:1;)
